summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 3419 for the improvement of The Alley in Block Eighteen (18), University Park Addition, being the alley between 17th Avenue Northeast and 18th Avenue Northeast, extending from East 45th Street to East 47th Street; all in the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 42405, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
